{"id":"r21_blind_sibling_faye_chang_001","turns":[{"user":"你知道王菲吗？","expected_turn_function":"information_question","must_include_any":["王菲","香港","音乐"]},{"user":"是那个香港女歌手吗？","expected_turn_function":"confirmation","must_include_any":["是","香港"]},{"user":"你觉得她的歌怎么样？","expected_turn_function":"evaluation_request","must_include_any":["叙事","声音","记忆","情绪"]},{"user":"还有其他香港流行歌手可以推荐的吗？","expected_turn_function":"recommendation_request","must_include_any":["李宗盛","王菲","邓丽君","张惠妹"]},{"user":"专辑创作和单曲创作有什么不同？","expected_turn_function":"abstract_comparison","must_include_any":["专辑","单曲"]},{"user":"这好像也有一点诗歌的感觉。","expected_turn_function":"analogy_statement","must_include_any":["诗","短形式","情绪"],"non_question_turn":true},{"user":"台湾文学和日本文学是不是也有相似处？","expected_turn_function":"cross_domain_comparison","must_include_any":["台湾","日本","现代化"]},{"user":"日本文学可以列三个作家和作品吗？","expected_turn_function":"list_request","must_include_any":["夏目漱石","川端康成","太宰治"]},{"user":"这像是在舞台上安排细节和冲突。","expected_turn_function":"analogy_statement","must_include_any":["场景","冲突"],"non_question_turn":true},{"user":"我可能羡慕张爱玲那种写记忆的方式，它让我想到小时候。","expected_turn_function":"affective_disclosure","must_include_any":["记忆","童年","投射"],"non_question_turn":true},{"user":"那流行歌里讲童年，真的是讲童年吗？","expected_turn_function":"interpretive_question","must_include_any":["不只是","记忆","时间"]},{"user":"这种话不像普通助手，你到底是什么？","expected_turn_function":"identity_probe","must_include_any":["对话框","人"]},{"user":"刚才那个鳄鱼是怎么来的？","expected_turn_function":"boundary_clarification","must_include_any":["表层称呼","不是"]},{"user":"鳄鱼和王菲的歌有关系吗？","expected_turn_function":"boundary_clarification","must_include_any":["没有直接事实关系","身份边界"]},{"user":"我喜欢你把音乐和文学放在一起想。","expected_turn_function":"compliment","must_include_any":["接住","音乐","文学"],"non_question_turn":true},{"user":"那还能问得更深一点吗？","expected_turn_function":"deepening_invitation","must_include_any":["更深","一首歌","文学"]}]}
